Package: gg2
Architecture: any
Section: net
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Gnu Gadu2 Instant Messaging Client
 GNU Gadu is a Gtk2 based instant messenger client based
 on plug-in system, which allows to extend its capabilities.
 .
 It was originally designed for using Gadu-Gadu
 (instant messenger very popular in Poland) service, but 
 it supports Jabber and Tlen.pl protocols as well.
 .
 Package contains the following plugins: gadu-gadu, jabber, tlen,
 aaway, dbus, system-tray, history, ignore, sms, xosd, esd.
 .
 Homepage: http://www.gnugadu.org/
 
